{"tid":808565,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來尿袋可以回收","createTime":"2018-09-06T12:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-06T12:22:06.000Z","uid":153311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ad4401acc6688e88b96fa360c0269af3bf91e910","tid":808565,"uid":153311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:14:02.000Z","msg":"尿袋由於內置充電池的關係，因此大家其實不能將之當作一般垃圾棄置，只因處理不當，會對環境及人體構成負面影響。早在 2005 年，香港政府已推行充電池回收計劃，可收回鋰離子（Li-ion）、鎳氫（NiMH）及鎳鎘（NiCd）3 種物料製造之便攜充電池，並設有逾 600 多個公眾回收點，詳細位置已上載至香港減廢網站，讓市民本閱。同時建議市民將充電池投放公眾回收點前，需做出以下 3 個步驟，減低充電池處理不當對環境及人體構成之影響。<br />\n<br />\n棄置尿袋的注意事項：<br />\n<br />\n將尿袋輸出、輸入端子貼上皺紋膠紙。<br />\n如尿袋有機會破損，需使用膠袋及膠紙，將外置電密封。<br />\n送到全港逾 600 多個公眾回收點棄置，如全線麥當勞餐廳、全線中國移動香港、87 個港鐵車站及 37 間 7-11 分店等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1903606/%E6%B6%88%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83+10+%E5%80%8B%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%8A%E6%A3%84%E7%BD%AE%E5%B0%BF%E8%A2%8B%E8%B2%BC%E5%A3%AB++%E9%81%8E%E7%86%B1%E8%A6%81%E5%8D%B3%E5%81%9C%E7%94%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1903606%2F%25E6%25B6%2588%25E5%25A7%2594%25E6%259C%2583%2B10%2B%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%25A3%2584%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E5%25B0%25BF%25E8%25A2%258B%25E8%25B2%25BC%25E5%25A3%25AB%2B%2B%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A6%2581%25E5%258D%25B3%25E5%2581%259C%25E7%2594%25A8&d=%2FkFLIGE7jG3W9RG5LudnmRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=b53b24e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1903606/%E6%B6%88%E5%A7%94%E6%9C%83+10+%E5%80%8B%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%8F%8A%E6%A3%84%E7%BD%AE%E5%B0%BF%E8%A2%8B%E8%B2%BC%E5%A3%AB++%E9%81%8E%E7%86%B1%E8%A6%81%E5%8D%B3%E5%81%9C%E7%94%A8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔知可以回收"},{"pid":"7f6e411943e3c7b04231a3bb8821809d89353f80","tid":808565,"uid":198583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T12:17:17.000Z","msg":"小米充電寶根本<span style=\"font-size: small;\">兒</span>牛逼死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" cl